      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个流程图，展示FinTech场景下LedgerService和PaymentGateway之间的认证与GPO交互流程。核心是从LedgerService发起用户认证，经过PaymentGateway去获取并解析GPO策略。",
